            <lang xml:lang="en">Tap a button. The always awake mode can be activated by: CONFIGURATION_SET / Parameter: 0x05 / Size: 0x01 (can’t be different from 1) /
Value: 0x03 (mode 3)</lang>
          </wakeupNote>
